AND SHAKE TO SHUFFLE MODE. THE NEW IPOD NANO ALSO FEATURES GENIUS MIXES, ALLOWING USERS TO AUTOMATICALLY CREATE SONG MIXES FROM THEIR MUSIC LIBRARIES. THE NEW IPOD

NANO PROVIDES UP TO 24 HOURS OF AUDIO PLAYBACK OR UP TO FIVE HOURS OF VIDEO PLAYBACK AND IS AVAILABLE IN 8GB AND 16GB CONFIGURATIONS IN A VARIETY OF COLORS.

