40,000 SONGS, 200 HOURS OF VIDEO, OR 25,000 PHOTOS. THE IPOD CLASSIC PROVIDES UP TO 36 HOURS OF AUDIO PLAYBACK OR UP TO SIX HOURS OF VIDEO PLAYBACK, FEATURES GENIUS TECHNOLOGY, AND INCLUDES A 2.5-INCH COLOR SCREEN THAT CAN DISPLAY ALBUM

