DRIVE CAPABLE OF STORING UP TO 200 HOURS OF VIDEO, 36,000 SONGS, 25,000 PHOTOS, OR A COMBINATION OF EACH AND IS COMPATIBLE WITH HIGH DEFINITION TELEVISIONS WITH RESOLUTION UP TO 1080P. APPLE TV CONNECTS TO A BROAD RANGE OF WIDESCREEN TELEVISIONS AND

