OPERATES, INCLUDING VARIOUS COUNTRIES WITHIN EUROPE AND ASIA AND CERTAIN STATES AND PROVINCES WITHIN NORTH AMERICA. ALTHOUGH THE COMPANY DOES NOT ANTICIPATE ANY MATERIAL ADVERSE EFFECTS BASED ON

