AS OF SEPTEMBER 26, 2009, THE COMPANY HAD TOTAL OUTSTANDING COMMITMENTS ON NONCANCELABLE OPERATING LEASES OF $1.9 BILLION, $1.5 BILLION OF WHICH RELATED TO THE LEASE OF RETAIL

