SUMMARY OF THE COMPANYS RSU ACTIVITY AND RELATED INFORMATION FOR THE THREE YEARS ENDED SEPTEMBER 26, 2009, IS AS FOLLOWS (IN THOUSANDS, EXCEPT PER SHARE AMOUNTS).

